Package pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1

Class MyMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1.MyMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - The type of keys maintained by this map.
V - The type of values associated with the keys.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<K,V>
public class MyMap<K,V> extends Object implements Map<K,V>
The MyMap class implements a custom Map data structure that stores keys and their corresponding values in two separate lists. Each key in the 'keys' list has a corresponding value in the 'values' list at the same index. The class supports basic operations such as adding, retrieving, and removing elements.
